    <category term="blog" scheme="https://singulair-x.github.io/tags/blog/"/>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p><a class="link"   href="https://obsidian.md/" >Obsidian<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a> 是一款非常强大的多平台本地笔记应用。相较于用 VS Code 或记事本写作，Obsidian具有实时阅览、大量写作辅助插件、支持双链和图谱等优势。本文将介绍如何配置 Obsidian 和 Hexo 以实现使用 Obsidian 进行日常的博客写作。</p><h2 id="建立仓库">建立仓库</h2><p>在仓库管理页选择“打开本地仓库”，将<code>博客\source</code>文件夹打开为仓库。Hexo 在渲染时会自动忽略前缀含<code>.</code>的文件夹，Obsidian 生成的<code>.obsidian</code>会被跳过。这就满足了最低需求。</p><p>在仓库内新建<code>images</code>文件夹，即可在文档中引入图片。例如：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">蒙娜丽莎</span>](<span class="link">/images/monalisa-100x100.jpg</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![[monalisa-100x100.jpg]] （需要后文插件支持）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><figure class="image-caption"><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="/images/monalisa-100x100.jpg"                      alt="蒙娜丽莎"                ><figcaption>蒙娜丽莎</figcaption></figure><h2 id="Hexo-强兼-Obsidian-语法">Hexo 强兼 Obsidian 语法</h2><p>Obsidian 有一些特有的语法，如标注框（Callouts）、WikiLink等。</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; [!info] 提示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 提示文本</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="callout" data-callout="info"><div class="callout-title"><div class="callout-title-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-info"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg></div><div class="callout-title-inner">提示</div></div><div class="callout-content"><p>提示文本</p></div></div><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[[a-new-start]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><a href="/2026/04/04/a-new-start.html">a-new-start</a></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![[monalisa-100x100.jpg]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><figure class="image-caption"><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="/images/monalisa-100x100.jpg"                      alt="monalisa-100x100.jpg"                ><figcaption>monalisa-100x100.jpg</figcaption></figure><h3 id="Callouts">Callouts</h3><ul><li>卸载<code>hexo-renderer-marked</code>：</li></ul><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm uninstall hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>安装<code>hexo-renderer-markdown-it</code></li></ul><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-markdown-it --save <span class="comment">#</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>安装<code>hexo-renderer-markdown-it</code>的配套插件：</li></ul><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install markdown-it-obsidian-callouts --save <span class="comment">#标注框支持：https://github.com/ebullient/markdown-it-obsidian-callouts</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>修改配置，在<code>_config.yml</code>里加入：（参考<a class="link"   href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-renderer-markdown-it" >hexojs/hexo-renderer-markdown-it<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>）<div class="code-container" data-rel="Yaml"><figure class="iseeu highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">markdown:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">preset:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;default&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">render:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">html:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">xhtmlOut:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">langPrefix:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;language-&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">breaks:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">linkify:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">typographer:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">quotes:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;“”‘’&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">enable_rules:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">disable_rules:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">plugins:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">markdown-it-obsidian-callouts</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">anchors:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">level:</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">collisionSuffix:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalinkClass:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;header-anchor&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalinkSide:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">permalinkSymbol:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;¶&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">case:</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">separator:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">images:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">lazyload:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">prepend_root:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">post_asset:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">inline:</span> <span class="literal">false</span>  <span class="comment"># https://markdown-it.github.io/markdown-it/#MarkdownIt.renderInline</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li></ul><p><strong>注意</strong>：标注框插件本身不带 css 样式，需要自行引入。以本站使用的 Redefine 主题为例，在<code>模板目录\source\css\common</code>里新建文件<code>callouts.css</code>，内容为<a class="link"   href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ebullient/markdown-it-obsidian-callouts/refs/heads/main/style/index.css" >index.css<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a> 。再修改<code>模板目录\source\css\style.styl</code>，增加：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Css"><figure class="iseeu highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">@require</span> <span class="string">&#x27;common/callouts.css&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h3 id="Wiki-Link">Wiki Link</h3><p>安装<code>hexo-obsidian-backlink</code>：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Bash"><figure class="iseeu highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-obsidian-backlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="callout" data-callout="warning"><div class="callout-title"><div class="callout-title-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-alert-triangle"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg></div><div class="callout-title-inner">Warning</div></div><div class="callout-content"><p>该插件对附件的处理与前述方式不同，可能需要自行修改代码。参考 <a class="link"   href="https://github.com/pondered/hexo-obsidian-backlink" >pondered/hexo-obsidian-backlink<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></p></div></div><p>类似的插件：</p><ul><li><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/Cyrusky/hexo-backlink" >Cyrusky/hexo-backlink<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></li><li><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/XiaoLinXiaoZhu/hexo-xlxz-imageRedirect" >XiaoLinXiaoZhu/hexo-xlxz-imageRedirect<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a></li></ul><h3 id="Markdown-it的其他插件">Markdown-it的其他插件</h3><p>在<code>_config.yml</code>中<code>hexo-renderer-markdown-it</code>的配置里增加：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Diff"><figure class="iseeu highlight diff"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">plugins:</span><br><span class="line">    - markdown-it-obsidian-callouts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   - markdown-it-footnote #脚注</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   - markdown-it-mark #高亮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="addition">+   - markdown-it-task-lists #Check List</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h3 id="反客为主">反客为主</h3><p>也可以反过来让 Obsidian 强兼 Hexo，可以利用<a class="link"   href="https://github.com/MathLeee/Ob2Hexo" >MathLeee/Ob2Hexo<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>等转换工具。</p><h2 id="推荐安装的-Obsidian-插件">推荐安装的 Obsidian 插件</h2><ul><li><code>Vault Nickname</code>： 给仓库设置别名（如改成<code>Blog</code>），需在所有需要显示 Nickname 的仓库里安装</li><li><code>Latex Suite</code>：加速输入 LaTex 公式</li><li><code>Easy Typing</code>：增强输入体验</li><li><code>Manual Sorting</code>：自定义排序</li><li><code>KaTex to MathJax</code>：便捷转换从 ChatGPT 的回答复制来的数学公式</li></ul>]]>
    </content>
